部署KDC
1.在namenode 安装
yum install krb5-server
yum install krb5-devel
yum install krb5-workstation
2.在datanode 上安装
yum install krb5-devel
yum install krb5-workstation

3.配置kdc以下3个文件
/etc/krb5.conf
/var/kerberos/krb5kdc/kdc.conf
/var/kerberos/krb5kdc/kadm5.acl
